Summary:    Client for OpenStack Reservation Service

Group:      Development/Python3
License:    Apache-2.0
Url:        http://docs.openstack.org/developer/%oname

Source:     https://tarballs.openstack.org/python-%oname/python-%oname-%version.tar.gz

